><li>This is not all the content in the plan. There are many still under development. We looking forward to presenting them to you in the continued development.</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Contents under development</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>More than 100 units are planned in 11 races.<br></li><li>Rune and equipment system would help you to fully use the potential of each unit.</li></ul>",
